    "body": "The second argument sets the column name. The first argument is a boolean that sets the original index as the index of the df ('ds' happens to be truthy).\r\n\r\n```\r\nIn [2]: pd.DatetimeIndex(['2019']).to_frame(True, 'ds')\r\nOut[2]:\r\n                   ds\r\n2019-01-01 2019-01-01\r\n``` \r\n\r\nhttps://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/reference/api/pandas.Index.to_frame.html"
